---
// Problem V3 — Le constat avec visuel à droite
---

<section class="py-24" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_420px] gap-16 items-center mb-16">

      <!-- Texte gauche -->
      <div>
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4" style="color: var(--accent);">Le constat</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight">
          Vous lancez des campagnes, vous testez l'IA, vous publiez sur LinkedIn…
          <span class="font-serif italic" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">et le ROI reste flou.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
          <strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">87 % des PME françaises</strong> n'ont pas encore engagé de projet IA structuré. Pas par manque d'envie, mais parce qu'avant de choisir le bon outil, il faut savoir précisément quel problème on cherche à résoudre. C'est exactement là que j'interviens.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Visuel droit — dispersion des outils (CSS) -->
      <div class="relative flex justify-center items-center">
        <div class="relative w-full max-w-sm aspect-square rounded-3xl overflow-hidden" style="background: var(--bg-tertiary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">

          <!-- Grille de fond légère -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(96,165,250,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(96,165,250,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 32px 32px;"></div>

          <!-- Badges d'outils épars — représentent le chaos -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0">
            <!-- CRM -->
            <div class="tool-badge float-anim" style="top:8%; left:10%; animation-delay:0s; --rot:-6deg; transform:rotate(-6deg);">
              <span class="dot" style="background:#f87171;"></span> CRM
            </div>
            <!-- Newsletter -->
            <div class="tool-badge float-anim" style="top:6%; right:8%; animation-delay:1.2s; --rot:5deg; transform:rotate(5deg);">
              <span class="dot" style="background:#60a5fa;"></span> Newsletter
            </div>
            <!-- Pub Méta -->
            <div class="tool-badge float-anim" style="top:28%; left:6%; animation-delay:0.6s; --rot:3deg; transform:rotate(3deg);">
              <span class="dot" style="background:#818cf8;"></span> Pub Méta
            </div>
            <!-- SEO -->
            <div class="tool-badge float-anim" style="top:32%; right:10%; animation-delay:1.8s; --rot:-4deg; transform:rotate(-4deg);">
              <span class="dot" style="background:#34d399;"></span> SEO
            </div>
            <!-- IA ? -->
            <div class="tool-badge float-anim" style="top:50%; left:18%; animation-delay:0.3s; --rot:-3deg; transform:rotate(-3deg);">
              <span class="dot" style="background:#fbbf24;"></span> IA ?
            </div>
            <!-- Google Ads -->
            <div class="tool-badge float-anim" style="top:52%; right:6%; animation-delay:1s; --rot:6deg; transform:rotate(6deg);">
              <span class="dot" style="background:#f472b6;"></span> Google Ads
            </div>
            <!-- LinkedIn -->
            <div class="tool-badge float-anim" style="top:72%; left:8%; animation-delay:1.4s; --rot:4deg; transform:rotate(4deg);">
              <span class="dot" style="background:#60a5fa;"></span> LinkedIn
            </div>
            <!-- Analytics -->
            <div class="tool-badge float-anim" style="top:74%; right:12%; animation-delay:0.8s; --rot:-5deg; transform:rotate(-5deg);">
              <span class="dot" style="background:#a78bfa;"></span> GA4
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Label bas -->
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-0 right-0 text-center text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] font-medium" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">Dispersion · Sans priorité</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 3 douleurs -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl card-hover" style="background: var(--bg-tertiary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-rose-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-rose-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Dispersion opérationnelle</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Trop d'actions lancées en parallèle, sans hiérarchie ni vision globale. Le temps file, l'effet de levier reste absent.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl card-hover" style="background: var(--bg-tertiary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">IA gadget</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Des outils IA testés pour la forme, sans intégration métier, sans mesure d'impact, sans ROI tangible.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl card-hover" style="background: var(--bg-tertiary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Pilotage difficile</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Pas de KPI clairs, pas de dashboards, des décisions prises au feeling plutôt qu'à la donnée.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
